==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chilled
<hw>Chilled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Hardened
on the surface or edge by chilling; <as>as, <ex>chilled</ex> iron; a
<ex>chilled</ex> wheel</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Paint.)</fld> <def>Having that cloudiness or
dimness of surface that is called
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>blooming</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chilli</ent>⟦br⟧
